1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,800
Before I bought this case, I honestly thought all luggage was pretty much the same - until I found out you can swap the colors of the handle and the wheels. You can match everything in one coordinated color, or mix different colors the way I did.

2
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:17,600
The wheels and handle come in seven colors in total, so you can pick a combination that matches your mood and your outfit for the day.

3
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:25,500
Now the material: the whole shell is aluminum-magnesium alloy, and the 200-plus rivets on the body are all hammered in by experienced craftsmen.

4
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:30,300
The four corners are reinforced with extra padding, so even the bumps and knocks of transit are no problem at all.

5
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:42,900
Look at the wheels - all made of TPE. Give one a light flick and it spins on its own for over a hundred seconds, which is really rare. Each wheel also has a built-in shock-absorbing spring, so it rolls dozens of times more smoothly.

6
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:48,400
Listen - almost completely silent. Order now and you'll also get an extra set of colored wheels free.
